生長期係超難辛苦，又刮又拮，想屌又要剃返乾淨先得，否則又刮損對方，沒完沒了。"},{"pid":"9ed89318028a31dc8b9ab282eef6618685c5b656","tid":6843,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T23:28:49.000Z","msg":"男人有毛先正囉 無毛好似女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe465a95f0ba80321e4d17ec0f3039082882d76","tid":6843,"uid":15812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T23:33:39.000Z","msg":"屎眼毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0400726818196ebcffda39b1a41c195a207011","tid":6843,"uid":18157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會剃鳩毛，因為覺得好焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔剃鳩毛 一到夏天出汗就會up住up住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a37357af48e649e40ef8fc6be9fc43d1b9209b","tid":6843,"uid":19955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a35a513644cc43babd4b0531f46492eb58c402de","tid":6843,"uid":19073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我會剃鳩毛，因為覺得好焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪好撚吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會剃鳩毛，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">陰莖留返 4mm 左右</span>，袋以下就用剃刀全剃。<br />\n之前試過全剃，比條女食同屌係好好feel . 因為唔係剃完即屌，好快生長左少少出來，好易刮損條女下體，試過兩次屌到出血先知咩事。仲有之後個 1/2mm 長度生長期係超難辛苦，又刮又拮，想屌又要剃返乾淨先得，否則又刮損對方，沒完沒了。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}